          <div style="font-size:11px; color:#aaa; font-family:monospace;">Dedication</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px; font-weight:800; color:#ea580c;">헌신</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:11px; color:#aaa; font-family:monospace;">Absorption</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px; font-weight:800; color:#ea580c;">몰두</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:9px; color:#ccc; text-align:right; margin-top:6px;">Schaufeli et al. (2002)</div>
    </div>

